7 Subject: Delinquency proceedings; minimum age
8 Statement of purpose of bill as introduced: This bill proposes to increase the
9 minimum age at which a child may be subject to juvenile delinquency
10 proceedings from 10 to 12.
11 An act relating to increasing the minimum age for delinquency proceedings
12 It is hereby enacted by the General Assembly of the State of Vermont:
13 Sec. 1. 33 V.S.A. § 5102 is amended to read:
